<lb n="0754a02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 808 [No. 809]</head>
<lb n="0754a03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛說犢子經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0754a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0754a05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">吳月<note n="0754001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">氏＝支【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">氏＝支【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754001"><lem wit="【大】">氏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">支</rdg></app>優婆塞支謙<note n="0754002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（初）＋譯【元】【明】</note><app n="0754002"><lem wit="【大】">譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">初譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0754a06" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT17p0754a0601">聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇<note n="0754003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">洹＝桓【三】【聖】</note><note n="0754003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洹＝桓【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0754003"><lem wit="【大】">洹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】">桓</rdg></app>阿那邠遲阿
<lb n="0754a07" ed="T"/>藍精舍。爾時佛<note n="0754004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遇風患＝患風【宮】</note><app n="0754004"><lem wit="【大】">遇風患</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">患風</rdg></app>當須牛乳。時有婆羅
<lb n="0754a08" ed="T"/>門大富去城不遠。時佛遣阿難言。汝往到婆
<lb n="0754a09" ed="T"/>羅門家從乞牛乳。阿難受教而往。<note n="0754005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754005"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0754006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至＝到【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至＝到【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754006"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">到</rdg></app>婆
<lb n="0754a10" ed="T"/>羅門家。婆羅門問阿難<note n="0754007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔言〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754007"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。來何所求。阿難
<lb n="0754a11" ed="T"/>言。如來向者少遇風患。<note n="0754008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">故遣我＝使我來【三】，故使我來【宮】</note><note n="0754008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故遣我＝使我來【宋】【元】【明】，＝故使我來【宮】</note><app n="0754008"><lem wit="【大】">故遣我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">使我來</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">故使我來</rdg></app>乞牛乳耳。
<lb n="0754a12" ed="T"/>婆羅門言。牛在彼間自&CB00590;取之。阿難即往到
<lb n="0754a13" ed="T"/>牛<note n="0754009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔群〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔群〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754009"><lem wit="【大】">群</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>所。<note n="0754010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有一〕－【三】，有一牸牛性常＝牛當【宮】</note><note n="0754010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有一牸牛性常＝牛當【宮】，〔有一〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0754010"><lem wit="【大】">有一牸牛。性常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">牛當</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">牸牛性常</rdg></app>弊惡無人能近。阿
<lb n="0754a14" ed="T"/>難即自思惟。我法不應自&CB00590;取牛乳。</p>
<lb n="0754a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0754a1501">爾時帝釋知阿難所念。即來化作婆羅門像
<lb n="0754a16" ed="T"/>在牛邊立。阿難往倩言。婆羅門為我&CB00590;取牛
<lb n="0754a17" ed="T"/><note n="0754011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乳＋（婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳）【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0754011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>乳＋（婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0754011"><lem wit="【大】">乳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">乳婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳</rdg></app>。語牛言。如來遇小風患。汝與乳<note n="0754012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">湩＝&CB05630;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">湩＝&CB05630;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754012"><lem wit="【大】">湩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&CB05630;</rdg></app>令如
<lb n="0754a18" ed="T"/>來服之。差者汝得福無量不可稱計。如來者
<lb n="0754a19" ed="T"/>是天上天下之大師也。<note n="0754013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＝常【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝常【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754013"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">常</rdg></app>以慈心憂念一切
<lb n="0754a20" ed="T"/>蠕動之類。欲令度脫一切苦惱。牛言。此手捫
<lb n="0754a21" ed="T"/>摸我乳。一何快耶。前兩乳取去。置後兩乳用
<lb n="0754a22" ed="T"/>遺我子。我子朝來未有所食。</p>
<lb n="0754a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0754a2301">爾時犢子在邊立住。聞有佛名即語母言。持
<lb n="0754a24" ed="T"/>我乳分盡用與佛。佛<note n="0754014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＋（是）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＋（是）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754014"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">者是</rdg></app>天上天下之大師也。
<lb n="0754a25" ed="T"/>甚難得值。我自食草飲水足得活耳。何以故。
<lb n="0754a26" ed="T"/>我先身以來常飲乳食。今<note n="0754015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＝作畜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝作畜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754015"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">作畜</rdg></app>生牛身亦復飲
<lb n="0754a27" ed="T"/>乳。世間愚癡者甚多無量。我先世時坐隨惡
<lb n="0754a28" ed="T"/>知識教不信佛經。使我作牛作馬經十六劫。
<lb n="0754a29" ed="T"/>而今乃得聞有佛名。持我所<note n="0754016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">食＋（乳）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＋（乳）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754016"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食乳</rdg></app>分盡用與佛
<pb n="0754b" id="T17.0808.0754b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0754b01" ed="T"/>滿器而去。令我後世智慧聰明得道如佛。阿
<lb n="0754b02" ed="T"/>難持乳還至佛所。</p>
<lb n="0754b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0754b0301">佛問阿難。彼牛母子有何言說。阿難言。大可
<lb n="0754b04" ed="T"/>怪也。牛先甚<note n="0754017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754017"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>弊惡不可得近。有一婆羅門
<lb n="0754b05" ed="T"/>為我&CB00590;乳。牛即調善。<note n="0754018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">母子＝子母【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">母子＝子母【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754018"><lem wit="【大】">母子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">子母</rdg></app>共說。佛言。此牛
<lb n="0754b06" ed="T"/>子母。先<note n="0754019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754019"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">世之</rdg></app>時不信佛經故。墮牛馬中經十六
<lb n="0754b07" ed="T"/>劫。今乃得悟聞有佛<note n="0754020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔名〕－【宋】【元】，明註曰南藏無名字</note><app n="0754020"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="【明】" wit="【南藏】">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0754021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＝使【宮】</note><app n="0754021"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">使</rdg></app><note n="0754022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【宮】</note><app n="0754022"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0754023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（我）＋慈【三】</note><note n="0754023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（我）＋慈【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0754023"><lem wit="【大】">慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">我慈</rdg></app>心以乳
<lb n="0754b08" ed="T"/>施佛。彼牛母子。後<note n="0754024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754024"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">身</rdg></app>當為彌勒佛<note n="0754025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（作）＋沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（作）＋沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754025"><lem wit="【大】">沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">作沙門</rdg></app>弟
<lb n="0754b09" ed="T"/>子得大羅漢。犢子死後當為我懸繒幡蓋。散
<lb n="0754b10" ed="T"/>華燒香受持經戒。過二十劫後當作佛。名乳
<lb n="0754b11" ed="T"/>光如來度脫一切。佛言。牛以好<note n="0754026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善心＝心善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善心＝心善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754026"><lem wit="【大】">善心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心善</rdg></app>意與佛
<lb n="0754b12" ed="T"/>乳故。度諸苦難。<note n="0754027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔後〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔後〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754027"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>得無量福報。以是因緣。
<lb n="0754b13" ed="T"/>佛不可不<note n="0754028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">信＝事【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">信＝事【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754028"><lem wit="【大】">信</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">事</rdg></app>。經不可不讀。道不可不學。普
<lb n="0754b14" ed="T"/>告天上天下皆悉令知。</p></div1>
